JSON -> XML:

- value as an actual XML prop name (FIXED: Changed to @value)
i.e.
{
    "Test": {
        "attribute": "a1",
        "value": "a2",
        "@value": "v" 
    }
} 
<Test attribute="a1" value="a2">
    v
</Test>

- value type check, must be str (ALREADY CHECKED)
i.e.
{
    "Test": null
}

- attribute-value pair must be str (FIXED: Throw type error if not type str)
i.e.
{
    "attribute": {}
}

- attribute must be lowercase str with no non-alpha characters (FIXED)